    ],
    "text": "Two Suspects Arrested Over Multiple Motorcycle Thefts \u2013 Negombo Divisional Crime Investigation Bureau",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      218.05,
      496.3,
      245.13
    ],
    "text": "Officers of the Negombo Divisional Crime Investigation Bureau initiated investigations into a series of motorcycle thefts reported to the Negombo Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      259.6,
      521.18,
      341.88
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 25.02.2026, investigation officers apprehended two suspects in connection with the said offences. The arrests were made in the Melisa Welihena Road area within the Minuwangoda Police Division and in the Angoda area of the Mulleriyawa Police Division. Two stolen motorcycles were also recovered during the operation. The suspects were subsequently handed over to the Negombo Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      356.44,
      494.97,
      383.52
    ],
    "text": "The arrested individuals, aged 37 and 47, are residents of the Minuwangoda and Angoda areas.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
